====Red (1996)====
{{main|Red (Masters)#Pikachu (1996)}}

An {{pkmn|multiverse|alternate universe}} version of Red, known as Red (1996), forms a sync pair with Pikachu as well. Red (1996) became a playable sync pair on [[Pokémon Day|February 27]], 2026. This version of Red is based on his [[Generation I]] design and exists as a separate person from the previously introduced Red.

